      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and its signature individual throttle bodies. The powertrain delivers urgent, linear throttle response all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. Crucially, the double-VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise gates with no synchro grind, paired with a limited-slip differential that remains tight. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the suspension bushings and cooling system have been refreshed, maintaining the razor-sharp turn-in and thermal efficiency this platform is known for.",
