      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior finish retains a deep, impressive shine, with only minor road peppering on the front fascia and a few light surface scratches that are consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the leather upholstery is supple with no tears, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system and heated seats, operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of tires installed last season. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision, providing a reliable and engaging driving experience. It is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that offers the perfect balance of luxury and dependability for its next owner.",
